                    </div>

                    <div class="newsletter  ">
                        <h6 class="fw-bold wht">Have a Question?</h6>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>203 Fake St. Mountain View, San Francisco, California, USA</p>
                        <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> 84+ 0935459488</p>
